Title: Tight compactly supported wavelet frames of arbitrarily high smoothness  
Author: Karlheinz Grochenig Amos Ron 
Keyword: Key Words: affine systems, frames, tight frames, multiresolution analysis, wavelets.  
Note: AMS (MOS) Subject Classifications: Primary 42C15, Secondary  This work was supported by the National Science Foundation under Grants DMS-9224748 and DMS 9626319, and by the U.S. Army Research Office under Contract DAAH04-95-1-0089.  
